headline: Nasdaq Announces End-of-Month Open Short Interest Positions in Nasdaq Stocks as of Settlement Date June 30, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, July 10, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- At the end of the settlement date of June 30, 2025, short interest in 3,257 Nasdaq Global MarketSM securities totaled 14,138,758,851 shares compared with 13,689,191,607 shares in 3,207 Global Market issues reported for the prior settlement date of June 13, 2025. The mid-June short interest represents 2.59 days compared with 2.32 days for the prior reporting period. Short interest in 1,636 securities on The Nasdaq Capital MarketSM totaled 2,790,159,938
